{"tid":1636001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 勇武快閃嘅初心忘記曬！快啲入嚟睇！","createTime":"2019-10-07T16:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:32:06.000Z","uid":167548,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e4394aea71b59f39fa62837a23269f040a546fdb","tid":1636001,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"堵路 裝修 所有野都是<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>增加管治成本</strong></span></span>！<br />\n前者癱瘓交通, 達至連鎖反應, 影響所有持份者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是我屌你老母自從緊急法之後, 夜晚街上面人都唔多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />車都沒幾架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堵路有咩撚用啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界無論是閒日定假期統一日頭繁忙時段堵佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10.4 政府製造宵禁情緒, 夜晚出動, 街上面人都唔多個, 有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界返屋企不被捕, 轉方向, 聽日返工放工時段開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜晚出嚟快閃, 除左被狗拉之外個效益是好唔化算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現時晚上街上面大多是自已友, 根本搞撚到班藍絲有錢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n車都唔見有幾多架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢出左宵禁堵嚟有閪樣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽朝起身各區快閃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且最重要是宵禁情況下,肯落街食花生大多是自已友, 次次都人小圍捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c394439c93c83ab83d4b3949751809c9b9b02fe5","tid":1636001,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76b8f7cf25c07824391f8c39e89bc8aaefb17d7","tid":1636001,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:05:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88a1fa474792976f687bf24b080c46b83ef8e82b","tid":1636001,"uid":281181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f3e7f702df52e0c86df1a34d5e42c7c79d0257c1","tid":1636001,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88a1fa474792976f687bf24b080c46b83ef8e82b","tid":1636001,"uid":281181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"推！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addb34ea26c06b75c14e9d76277b6d6d66de3e2f","tid":1636001,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ceeb7e12a9008e9598e93d6266907d831b722ca","tid":1636001,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"借個位黎用吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全港最黃嘅光時網物平台於10月7日上線啦!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629141</a>"},{"pid":"b5d48c126cc58c08d9f88b52156808ef45adcf61","tid":1636001,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"推"}]}